## Notes

- Jupyter is installed but disabled by default.
- `mistral.rs` is installed but requires a profile under `/etc/acabos/inference/` before use.
- `qdrant`, `localai`, and `comfyui` are validated on first boot and enabled only if they pass runtime checks.
- Hugepages are not reserved by default.

See `FIRST-STEPS.md` for enablement and day-one usage instructions.
